programme.title: Live Test Cricket
programme.sub-title: England v West Indies: First Test Day Two.
programme.desc: England v West Indies. Coverage of the second day of the First Test, which takes place at Edgbaston - the first-ever day-night Test to be held in England. The tourists last visited for a Test series in 2012, when Andrew Strauss's men came out as 2-0 winners from the three-game series. The Windies did salvage some pride in the Third Test on this ground, however, securing a draw(c)

programme.title: Live Solheim Cup Golf
programme.desc: Coverage of the first day's play at the Des Moines Golf and Country Club, Iowa, where the 15th staging of the biennial women's tournament between Europe and the United States gets under way with the opening foursomes and fourballs. The US are defending the title after their 14 1/2- 13 1/2 victory two years ago at St Leon-Rot Golf Club in Germany, when they overcame a six-point deficit going into the final day singles to complete the biggest comeback in the tournament's history
